1
00:00:09,666 --> 00:00:11,466
Narrator: HEAVENS ARENA.

2
00:00:11,500 --> 00:00:14,666
THE 251‐STORY BUILDING

3
00:00:14,666 --> 00:00:17,766
WHICH STANDS 991 METERS TALL

4
00:00:17,800 --> 00:00:20,333
‐ IS A MECCA FOR FIGHTERS.
‐ ( crowd cheering )

5
00:00:20,333 --> 00:00:24,333
WHEN COMBATANTS WIN A FIGHT,
THEY MAY ADVANCE BY ONE CLASS

6
00:00:24,400 --> 00:00:26,833
AND RECEIVE
A CORRESPONDING REWARD.

7
00:00:26,900 --> 00:00:28,600
AFTER REACHING THE 100th FLOOR,

8
00:00:28,633 --> 00:00:30,966
THEY ARE ASSIGNED
A PRIVATE ROOM.

9
00:00:31,000 --> 00:00:34,333
AND THOSE CONTESTANTS WHO ARE
SKILLED AND FORTUNATE ENOUGH

10
00:00:34,400 --> 00:00:36,100
TO REACH THE 200th FLOOR

11
00:00:36,133 --> 00:00:39,400
EARN THE RIGHT TO CHALLENGE
THE STRONGEST FIGHTERS,

12
00:00:39,433 --> 00:00:43,500
THE FLOOR MASTERS, IN AN INTENSE
BATTLE FOR SURVIVAL.

13
00:00:43,566 --> 00:00:46,100
THIS IS, WITHOUT A DOUBT,

14
00:00:46,133 --> 00:00:49,233
THE BEST STAGE
A WARRIOR COULD ASK FOR.

15
00:00:51,566 --> 00:00:53,500
♪

16
00:00:57,066 --> 00:01:00,006
( singing in Japanese )

17
00:02:15,016 --> 00:02:16,783
♪

18
00:02:16,816 --> 00:02:19,783
Sadaso: TODAY, I'LL BEAT
KILLUA FOR MY SIXTH WIN.

19
00:02:19,816 --> 00:02:23,183
TOMORROW, I'LL BEAT GON
FOR MY SEVENTH WIN.

20
00:02:23,183 --> 00:02:28,350
AFTER THAT, ALL I'LL NEED TO DO
IS FIND THREE MORE SUCKERS.

21
00:02:28,383 --> 00:02:29,550
HEH HEH HEH.

22
00:02:29,616 --> 00:02:31,683
THEN I'LL BE A FLOOR MASTER.

23
00:02:31,716 --> 00:02:34,683
WITH THE KIND OF FAME
AND FORTUNE THAT'LL GET ME,

24
00:02:34,716 --> 00:02:37,350
I'LL BE SET
FOR THE REST OF MY LIFE.

25
00:02:37,383 --> 00:02:39,016
( gasps )

26
00:02:41,450 --> 00:02:43,516
Killua: YOU MOVE, YOU DIE.

27
00:02:43,516 --> 00:02:45,716
YOU USE NEN, AND YOU DIE.

28
00:02:45,783 --> 00:02:47,983
MAKE A SOUND, AND YOU DIE.

29
00:02:48,016 --> 00:02:51,650
IF YOU UNDERSTAND,
CLOSE YOUR EYES.

30
00:02:52,516 --> 00:02:54,216
DO YOU SEE WHAT HAPPENS

31
00:02:54,283 --> 00:02:56,216
WHEN YOU BREAK YOUR PROMISES?

32
00:02:57,350 --> 00:02:59,683
IF YOU DO, OPEN YOUR EYES,

33
00:02:59,683 --> 00:03:02,856
LOOK AT ME IN THE MIRROR,
AND LISTEN CAREFULLY.

34
00:03:06,956 --> 00:03:11,523
DON'T EVER SHOW YOUR DIRTY FACE
IN FRONT OF US AGAIN.

35
00:03:11,523 --> 00:03:13,990
YOU'LL KEEP THIS PROMISE.

36
00:03:14,023 --> 00:03:15,956
♪

37
00:03:18,823 --> 00:03:19,990
( overlapping chatter )

38
00:03:20,023 --> 00:03:22,223
Narrator: THERE ARE MANY
WHO WOULD RESORT

39
00:03:22,290 --> 00:03:26,190
TO USING UNDERHANDED TACTICS
TO BECOME A FLOOR MASTER.

40
00:03:26,190 --> 00:03:29,856
GON, ON THE OTHER HAND,
HAS BEEN FIERCELY CONCENTRATING

41
00:03:29,890 --> 00:03:32,156
ON IMPROVING HIS NEN
AND GROWING STRONGER,

42
00:03:32,190 --> 00:03:36,056
AND TONIGHT, HE HAS
HIS BATTLE WITH SADASO.

43
00:03:37,190 --> 00:03:40,623
Sadaso: HIS EYES,
THEY BELONG TO SOMEONE

44
00:03:40,656 --> 00:03:43,323
WHO LIVES IN THE WORLD
OF DARKNESS.

45
00:03:44,490 --> 00:03:45,956
I WAS FILLED WITH DESPAIR.

46
00:03:45,990 --> 00:03:48,356
I COULD SENSE
THE DIFFERENCE IN STRENGTH

47
00:03:48,356 --> 00:03:49,856
THE SECOND OUR EYES MET.

48
00:03:49,856 --> 00:03:52,390
IT WAS CLEAR
THAT HE WAS THE PREDATOR,

49
00:03:52,456 --> 00:03:54,190
AND I WAS HIS PREY. ( shudders )

50
00:03:54,190 --> 00:03:57,723
IT WAS A HUGE MISTAKE
TO UNDERESTIMATE HIM.

51
00:03:57,790 --> 00:04:00,330
HE ISN'T JUST
SOME NORMAL KID. HEH.

52
00:04:02,630 --> 00:04:04,130
I DON'T WANT TO DIE,

53
00:04:04,163 --> 00:04:06,796
SO I'M GETTING THE HELL
OUT OF HERE. ( shudders )

54
00:04:06,830 --> 00:04:08,230
YOU SHOULD BE CAREFUL.

55
00:04:08,296 --> 00:04:11,463
HE'LL BE COMING AFTER
YOU GUYS NEXT. ( shudders )

56
00:04:11,496 --> 00:04:13,630
( phone line beeping )

57
00:04:15,396 --> 00:04:17,363
( beeping continues )

58
00:04:20,396 --> 00:04:21,530
( phone beeps )

59
00:04:21,563 --> 00:04:23,896
Gido: NOW WHAT?

60
00:04:24,863 --> 00:04:26,730
Riehlvelt: WELL, I'M STILL IN,

61
00:04:26,796 --> 00:04:30,396
AND I'M WILLING
TO DO WHATEVER IT TAKES.

62
00:04:30,463 --> 00:04:32,796
I'M ALMOST A FLOOR MASTER.

63
00:04:32,830 --> 00:04:35,363
10 VICTORIES ON THIS FLOOR,

64
00:04:35,396 --> 00:04:38,796
AND YOU'RE ALLOWED
TO CHALLENGE A FLOOR MASTER.

65
00:04:38,829 --> 00:04:43,296
IF YOU WIN, YOU GET
AN ENTIRE FLOOR TO YOURSELF.

66
00:04:43,330 --> 00:04:45,363
( Gido shudders )

67
00:04:45,396 --> 00:04:48,530
Riehlvelt: AND AS SOON
AS THAT TITLE IS IN YOUR HAND,

68
00:04:48,563 --> 00:04:50,830
YOU CAN LECTURE,
TEACH, AND ADVISE,

69
00:04:50,863 --> 00:04:54,230
OR START UP
A MARTIAL ARTS SCHOOL.

70
00:04:54,296 --> 00:04:58,696
FOR THE REST OF YOUR LIFE,
YOU'VE GOT IT MADE.

71
00:04:58,696 --> 00:05:00,503
Gido: DO YOU THINK THAT KID'S

72
00:05:00,536 --> 00:05:03,136
GONNA COME BACK HERE
TO THREATEN US?

73
00:05:03,170 --> 00:05:07,003
Riehlvelt: THE BOY HAS NO CLUE
WHAT MY ABILITIES ARE.

74
00:05:07,036 --> 00:05:09,203
AS LONG AS WE'RE
CAREFUL ABOUT IT,

75
00:05:09,236 --> 00:05:12,203
WE SHOULD BE ABLE
TO HANDLE HIM QUITE EASILY.

76
00:05:12,236 --> 00:05:14,036
‐ Killua: YOU'RE WRONG.
‐ ( both gasp )

77
00:05:16,203 --> 00:05:19,570
Killua: IT DOESN'T REALLY
MATTER WHAT YOUR ABILITIES ARE.

78
00:05:19,636 --> 00:05:21,703
( Gido gasps )

79
00:05:22,736 --> 00:05:24,536
Killua: THERE'S NO RUSH,
YOU SEE.

80
00:05:24,570 --> 00:05:27,136
‐ I CAN ALWAYS GET TO YOU...
‐ ( both gasp )

81
00:05:28,036 --> 00:05:31,003
WHENEVER AND WHEREVER I WANT.

82
00:05:31,036 --> 00:05:34,003
AT NIGHT, WHEN YOU'RE
SOUND ASLEEP IN YOUR BED,

83
00:05:34,036 --> 00:05:38,470
WHEN YOU'RE TAKING A CRAP,
RIGHT?

84
00:05:38,503 --> 00:05:40,636
♪

85
00:05:48,670 --> 00:05:50,003
LISTEN UP.

86
00:05:50,036 --> 00:05:52,303
YOU SHOULD FOLLOW THE RULES.

87
00:05:52,336 --> 00:05:57,870
WITHOUT THE RULES, THE ONLY ONES
BENEFITTING WOULD BE US.

88
00:06:06,343 --> 00:06:07,843
( Riehlvelt chuckles )

89
00:06:08,710 --> 00:06:10,510
AS I WAS SAYING,

90
00:06:10,543 --> 00:06:12,010
CHEATING IS A TERRIBLE IDEA.

91
00:06:12,043 --> 00:06:14,676
A FAIR FIGHT IS THE WAY TO GO.

92
00:06:14,710 --> 00:06:16,076
Gido: RIGHT.

93
00:06:16,143 --> 00:06:18,043
♪

94
00:06:21,910 --> 00:06:24,310
Referee: SADASO'S TIME IS UP!

95
00:06:24,343 --> 00:06:26,510
GON WINS BY DEFAULT!

96
00:06:26,543 --> 00:06:28,676
‐ ( crowd booing )
‐ Man: WHAT?! AGAIN?!

97
00:06:28,710 --> 00:06:31,843
Man #2: YEAH, WHAT THE HELL
IS SADASO DOING?

98
00:06:32,976 --> 00:06:34,876
♪

99
00:06:53,210 --> 00:06:57,843
Wing: ALL RIGHT. SO TODAY,
GON WILL BE FIGHTING GIDO.

100
00:06:57,876 --> 00:06:59,243
AFTER THAT, OF COURSE,

101
00:06:59,310 --> 00:07:02,416
KILLUA WILL BE GOING UP
AGAINST RIEHLVELT.

102
00:07:02,483 --> 00:07:04,250
ARE YOU BOTH FEELING ALL RIGHT?

103
00:07:04,316 --> 00:07:05,550
Both: YES, SIR!

104
00:07:05,550 --> 00:07:09,083
Wing: NOW, THIS WILL BE
YOUR SECOND MATCH AGAINST GIDO,

105
00:07:09,150 --> 00:07:12,816
SO I DOUBT YOU'LL
REQUIRE MUCH ADVICE.

106
00:07:12,850 --> 00:07:14,850
HAVE YOU SETTLED ON A STRATEGY?

107
00:07:14,883 --> 00:07:17,716
Gon: YES. I, UH, THINK I HAVE.

108
00:07:17,750 --> 00:07:19,183
WELL, HERE'S THE THING.

109
00:07:21,883 --> 00:07:24,550
MY STRATEGY IS TO USE THAT.

110
00:07:24,550 --> 00:07:25,916
Killua: HUH?

111
00:07:25,983 --> 00:07:28,050
Wing: YES, I UNDERSTAND.

112
00:07:28,083 --> 00:07:29,883
( crowd cheering )

113
00:07:31,716 --> 00:07:34,383
Cocco: THE REMATCH
YOU'VE ALL BEEN WAITING FOR

114
00:07:34,416 --> 00:07:37,716
IS FINALLY HERE,
GIDO VERSUS GON!

115
00:07:37,750 --> 00:07:40,250
THEIR LAST MATCH
LANDED GON IN THE HOSPITAL,

116
00:07:40,316 --> 00:07:43,750
BUT THERE'S NO TELLING
WHAT WE'RE IN FOR THIS TIME!

117
00:07:43,816 --> 00:07:46,883
FOR TODAY'S MATCH,
GON IS CARRYING A FISHING ROD.

118
00:07:47,983 --> 00:07:50,383
BUT HOW EXACTLY
DOES HE PLAN TO USE IT?

119
00:07:50,383 --> 00:07:53,583
WILL HE BE INCORPORATING IT
INTO HIS FIGHTING STYLE?

120
00:07:53,650 --> 00:07:55,150
LET'S FIND OUT.

121
00:07:55,183 --> 00:08:00,390
Referee: THIS IS A POINTS AND
K. O. SYSTEM, NO TIME LIMIT!

122
00:08:00,423 --> 00:08:01,390
BEGIN!

123
00:08:02,890 --> 00:08:06,923
Cocco: RIGHT OFF THE BAT,
GON TAKES OFF IN A MAD DASH!

124
00:08:06,990 --> 00:08:09,390
BUT IT LOOKS LIKE GIDO
WAS PREPARED FOR THIS.

125
00:08:09,390 --> 00:08:12,223
HE'S ALREADY RESPONDING
WITH HIS TORNADO TOP.

126
00:08:13,556 --> 00:08:15,223
IF GON CHARGES IN,

127
00:08:15,223 --> 00:08:18,690
HE'LL BE IN THE SAME POSITION
HE WAS LAST TIME.

128
00:08:18,723 --> 00:08:21,156
Gon: HE'S WAY AHEAD OF ME.

129
00:08:21,190 --> 00:08:22,990
( Gido laughs )

130
00:08:23,023 --> 00:08:24,723
I KNOW WHAT YOU'RE THINKING.

131
00:08:24,723 --> 00:08:26,156
ONCE I'VE STARTED SPINNING,

132
00:08:26,190 --> 00:08:28,556
IT'S VIRTUALLY IMPOSSIBLE
TO STOP ME.

133
00:08:28,556 --> 00:08:31,223
THE ONLY LOGICAL COURSE
WOULD BE TO HIT ME

134
00:08:31,256 --> 00:08:34,923
WITH A PREEMPTIVE ATTACK
BEFORE I EVEN START.

135
00:08:34,990 --> 00:08:38,223
WELL, IF YOU'RE NOT GOING
TO MAKE A MOVE, I WILL!

136
00:08:38,256 --> 00:08:40,723
SHOTGUN BLUES!

137
00:08:41,723 --> 00:08:45,223
Gon: HE CAN FIRE OFF
HIS TOPS MIDSPIN?

138
00:08:45,223 --> 00:08:46,356
Gido: AS YOU CAN SEE,

139
00:08:46,390 --> 00:08:49,090
THIS TECHNIQUE IS NOTHING
LIKE THE BATTLE WALTZ.

140
00:08:49,156 --> 00:08:51,890
ALL MY TOPS WILL BE
AIMING RIGHT FOR YOU.

141
00:08:51,923 --> 00:08:54,390
YOU'LL NEVER BE ABLE
TO DODGE THEM ALL.

142
00:08:54,423 --> 00:08:55,390
Gon: REN!

143
00:08:55,423 --> 00:08:57,390
♪

144
00:08:59,763 --> 00:09:00,830
Gido: WHAT?

145
00:09:00,863 --> 00:09:02,496
Man: WHOA! HE STOPPED THEM!

146
00:09:02,530 --> 00:09:04,563
Man #2: DID YOU JUST SEE THAT?

147
00:09:04,596 --> 00:09:05,830
Man #3: OH, WOW.

148
00:09:05,863 --> 00:09:08,063
Cocco: THAT WAS INCREDIBLE!

149
00:09:08,063 --> 00:09:10,396
GON JUST BLOCKED
THE TOPS HEAD‐ON!

150
00:09:10,430 --> 00:09:14,730
HE IS NOT THE SAME COMPETITOR
HE WAS TWO MONTHS AGO.

151
00:09:17,663 --> 00:09:19,596
( Gido groans ) DAMN.

152
00:09:19,663 --> 00:09:21,896
HIS NEN DEFENSES
HAVE SHOT WAY UP.

153
00:09:21,896 --> 00:09:24,896
WILL MY TOPS STILL BE
ENOUGH TO BEAT HIM?

154
00:09:24,930 --> 00:09:28,396
Killua: THOSE TOPS
WERE COMING STRAIGHT AT HIM.

155
00:09:28,396 --> 00:09:30,063
WITH HIS REFLEXES,

156
00:09:30,063 --> 00:09:33,530
GON COULD HAVE KNOCKED THEM
ALL DOWN WITH HIS FISHING ROD,

157
00:09:33,563 --> 00:09:36,330
BUT HE CHOSE TO GO
WITH REN INSTEAD,

158
00:09:36,363 --> 00:09:40,096
AND THAT DID WAY MORE
PSYCHOLOGICAL DAMAGE TO GIDO.

159
00:09:40,163 --> 00:09:42,063
♪

160
00:09:42,063 --> 00:09:46,230
HE MUST BE THINKING ABOUT HOW
THEY USED ZUSHI TO BLACKMAIL US,

161
00:09:46,263 --> 00:09:47,896
AND HE'S FURIOUS.

162
00:09:47,896 --> 00:09:49,896
Gon: OKAY, IT'S MY TURN NOW.

163
00:09:49,930 --> 00:09:54,030
Cocco: I WONDER WHAT TECHNIQUE
GON WILL USE THIS TIME, FOLKS!

164
00:09:54,063 --> 00:09:56,730
Gido: HE'S USING A FISHING ROD,

165
00:09:56,730 --> 00:09:59,030
AND THAT CAN
ONLY MEAN ONE THING.

166
00:09:59,063 --> 00:10:04,170
HE'LL TRY TO SNAG MY CLOTHES
AND BRING MY SPINNING TO A HALT.

167
00:10:04,170 --> 00:10:06,970
BUT IT'S NOT GOING
TO BE THAT EASY.

168
00:10:07,003 --> 00:10:08,870
♪

169
00:10:13,836 --> 00:10:16,870
Cocco: THERE IT IS!
HE'S GOING STRAIGHT FOR GIDO!

170
00:10:16,936 --> 00:10:19,436
Gido: HEE HEE HEE! I KNEW IT.

171
00:10:19,470 --> 00:10:21,670
NOT GONNA HAPPEN!

172
00:10:22,603 --> 00:10:24,303
( gasps )

173
00:10:25,370 --> 00:10:26,336
Cocco: OH, NO!

174
00:10:26,370 --> 00:10:27,970
HIS ATTACK MISSED ITS TARGET!

175
00:10:28,003 --> 00:10:31,303
( Gido cackles )
WHAT WERE YOU EVEN AIMING AT?

176
00:10:35,103 --> 00:10:36,603
( Gon yells )

177
00:10:36,636 --> 00:10:37,770
Gido: WHAT THE...

178
00:10:39,270 --> 00:10:41,003
Cocco: UNBELIEVABLE!

179
00:10:41,003 --> 00:10:44,636
GON FLIPPED THE FLOOR TILE
AND GIDO ALONG WITH IT!

180
00:10:44,670 --> 00:10:46,770
( Gido yells )

181
00:10:51,036 --> 00:10:53,003
( groans )

182
00:10:53,036 --> 00:10:54,170
( yelps )

183
00:10:56,036 --> 00:10:58,436
( Gon grunts )

184
00:10:58,470 --> 00:10:59,643
( Gido shuddering )

185
00:10:59,676 --> 00:11:01,176
( Gon yells )

186
00:11:01,210 --> 00:11:02,176
Gido: NO! WAIT!

187
00:11:05,010 --> 00:11:06,976
♪

188
00:11:10,010 --> 00:11:14,510
Cocco: G‐GON HAS JUST BROKEN
GIDO'S STEEL PROSTHETIC LEG,

189
00:11:14,510 --> 00:11:15,976
MAKING IT VERY UNLIKELY

190
00:11:16,010 --> 00:11:18,943
THAT HE'LL BE ABLE
TO CONTINUE THE FIGHT.

191
00:11:18,976 --> 00:11:21,676
Gon: IF YOU GUYS
RESORT TO ANY MEANS,

192
00:11:21,676 --> 00:11:23,676
THEN WE WON'T
HOLD BACK EITHER.

193
00:11:23,710 --> 00:11:26,710
AND IF YOU EVEN
TOUCH ZUSHI EVER AGAIN,

194
00:11:26,776 --> 00:11:30,610
NEXT TIME I SEE YOU,
I'LL BREAK YOUR FACE IN HALF!

195
00:11:30,643 --> 00:11:33,143
( Gido shuddering )

196
00:11:35,510 --> 00:11:37,676
Referee: THE WINNER IS GON!

197
00:11:37,710 --> 00:11:39,043
( crowd cheering )

198
00:11:39,110 --> 00:11:41,676
Cocco: GON WAS
FINALLY ABLE TO AVENGE

199
00:11:41,710 --> 00:11:43,676
HIS INITIAL LOSS TO GIDO.

200
00:11:43,676 --> 00:11:47,876
HIS RECORD ON THE 200th FLOOR
IS NOW TWO TO ONE!

201
00:11:47,943 --> 00:11:50,210
♪

202
00:11:56,710 --> 00:12:00,216
Killua: ALL RIGHT.
GUESS I'M UP NEXT.

203
00:12:04,448 --> 00:12:07,648
Cocco: AND NOW FOR
THE MAIN EVENT OF THE DAY,

204
00:12:07,681 --> 00:12:09,681
KILLUA VERSUS RIEHLVELT!

205
00:12:09,748 --> 00:12:12,948
SINCE SADASO FORFEITED
THE PREVIOUS MATCH,

206
00:12:12,981 --> 00:12:16,748
THIS WILL TECHNICALLY BE
KILLUA'S 200th‐FLOOR DEBUT.

207
00:12:16,781 --> 00:12:20,281
WHAT KIND OF STRATEGY
ARE WE ABOUT TO SEE NOW?

208
00:12:20,315 --> 00:12:23,281
Killua: YOU DO REALIZE THAT YOU
BROKE YOUR PROMISE FIRST.

209
00:12:23,315 --> 00:12:25,915
THERE'S NO WAY
I'LL LET YOU WIN NOW.

210
00:12:28,681 --> 00:12:30,148
Sadaso: HIS EYES,

211
00:12:30,181 --> 00:12:34,281
THEY BELONG TO SOMEONE WHO LIVES
IN THE WORLD OF DARKNESS.

212
00:12:34,315 --> 00:12:38,115
Riehlvelt: "SOMEONE WHO LIVES
IN THE WORLD OF DARKNESS"?

213
00:12:39,315 --> 00:12:43,015
SO WHAT IF THIS BRAT IS
A PROFESSIONAL ASSASSIN?

214
00:12:43,081 --> 00:12:45,615
HEAVENS ARENA IS MY TURF.

215
00:12:45,615 --> 00:12:47,648
IT'S TIME FOR ME TO SHOW HIM

216
00:12:47,681 --> 00:12:52,915
THAT WITHIN THE FOUR SIDES
OF THIS SQUARE STAGE, I RULE!

217
00:12:52,948 --> 00:12:55,081
( crowd cheering )

218
00:12:56,948 --> 00:12:59,681
Zushi: GO, KILLUA!
YOU CAN DO IT!

219
00:12:59,748 --> 00:13:02,021
( Gon sighs )

220
00:13:04,021 --> 00:13:09,288
Referee: THIS IS A POINTS AND
K. O. SYSTEM! NO TIME LIMIT!

221
00:13:09,288 --> 00:13:10,255
BEGIN!

222
00:13:12,655 --> 00:13:13,988
Riehlvelt: HE VANISHED?

223
00:13:19,288 --> 00:13:20,755
BEHIND ME.

224
00:13:20,788 --> 00:13:22,321
AURA BURST!

225
00:13:24,955 --> 00:13:28,955
Cocco: RIEHLVELT BOOSTED
OUT OF HARM'S WAY!

226
00:13:28,988 --> 00:13:32,088
HE PROPELS HIS WHEELCHAIR
BY RELEASING HIS STORED AURA,

227
00:13:32,121 --> 00:13:35,321
GUIDING IT
TO WHEREVER HE WANTS TO GO.

228
00:13:35,355 --> 00:13:38,021
Killua: I JUMPED TOO HIGH.

229
00:13:38,088 --> 00:13:40,788
Riehlvelt: WHEW. THAT WAS CLOSE.

230
00:13:44,855 --> 00:13:47,988
TWO‐HEADED SNAKE,
TWIN SERPENTS!

231
00:13:54,688 --> 00:13:56,788
SONG OF DEFENSE!

232
00:13:58,188 --> 00:14:01,595
Cocco: THERE IT IS, FOLKS,
RIEHLVELT'S SONG OF DEFENSE!

233
00:14:01,628 --> 00:14:03,661
HE PROTECTS HIMSELF
WITH TWO WHIPS

234
00:14:03,695 --> 00:14:05,195
MOVING AT
RIDICULOUSLY HIGH SPEEDS,

235
00:14:05,261 --> 00:14:08,361
THEN WAITS PATIENTLY
FOR HIS CHANCE TO STRIKE!

236
00:14:09,461 --> 00:14:10,495
Riehlvelt: HEH.

237
00:14:10,528 --> 00:14:13,095
YOU PLANNED TO ATTACK FIRST
AND TAKE THE LEAD.

238
00:14:13,128 --> 00:14:15,028
TOO BAD
THAT DIDN'T WORK FOR YOU.

239
00:14:15,095 --> 00:14:16,928
NOW THAT I'VE TAKEN THIS STANCE,

240
00:14:16,961 --> 00:14:19,461
THERE IS NO WAY
YOU COULD POSSIBLY WIN!

241
00:14:19,495 --> 00:14:20,795
Killua: WHY'S THAT?

242
00:14:20,795 --> 00:14:23,795
Riehlvelt:
IT'S OBVIOUS, ISN'T IT?

243
00:14:23,795 --> 00:14:25,595
NO NORMAL PERSON ON THE PLANET

244
00:14:25,628 --> 00:14:27,661
CAN KEEP UP
WITH THESE TWO WHIPS!

245
00:14:27,695 --> 00:14:29,361
AND ON THIS LITTLE PLATFORM,

246
00:14:29,428 --> 00:14:32,095
THERE'S NOWHERE
YOU CAN RUN AND HIDE!

247
00:14:32,128 --> 00:14:33,995
♪

248
00:14:36,461 --> 00:14:37,861
( Killua sighs )

249
00:14:45,295 --> 00:14:47,795
Riehlvelt: TAKE THIS!

250
00:14:54,695 --> 00:14:56,661
Killua: YEAH?
WELL, I'M NOT NORMAL.

251
00:14:56,695 --> 00:14:57,928
SORRY 'BOUT THAT.

252
00:14:57,961 --> 00:15:00,128
Riehlvelt: WHAT?!

253
00:15:00,128 --> 00:15:01,201
FINE, THEN.

254
00:15:01,268 --> 00:15:03,335
♪

255
00:15:07,601 --> 00:15:08,801
THUNDER SERPENT!

256
00:15:08,835 --> 00:15:11,335
( gasping )

257
00:15:14,835 --> 00:15:16,335
( Gon sighs )

258
00:15:20,268 --> 00:15:22,201
Riehlvelt:
I'M SURPRISED, KILLUA.

259
00:15:22,268 --> 00:15:24,301
YOU'RE THE FIRST PERSON
I'VE FOUGHT

260
00:15:24,335 --> 00:15:26,335
WHO COULD SEE
MY WHIPS IN MOTION,

261
00:15:26,368 --> 00:15:28,801
SO I'VE GOT
A LITTLE PRESENT FOR YOU.

262
00:15:28,835 --> 00:15:32,201
THOSE TWO WHIPS TOGETHER
CARRY ONE MILLION VOLTS,

263
00:15:32,268 --> 00:15:36,868
MORE THAN ENOUGH TO PARALYZE
AND INCAPACITATE A GIANT.

264
00:15:36,935 --> 00:15:39,501
ANYONE FOOLISH ENOUGH
TO RESIST MY WHIPS

265
00:15:39,535 --> 00:15:42,201
WILL FALL VICTIM
TO THE MIGHTY THUNDER SERPENT!

266
00:15:42,268 --> 00:15:44,768
WHAAH!

267
00:15:46,335 --> 00:15:48,501
Killua: I'M TRAINED
TO ENDURE TORTURE,

268
00:15:48,535 --> 00:15:50,435
SO ELECTRICITY WON'T WORK.

269
00:15:50,468 --> 00:15:52,435
IT HAS NO EFFECT ON ME.

270
00:15:52,468 --> 00:15:54,668
I MEAN, I CAN TOLERATE IT,

271
00:15:54,701 --> 00:15:57,301
BUT IT ISN'T LIKE
IT MAKES ME HAPPY.

272
00:15:57,301 --> 00:16:00,001
IT STILL REALLY HURTS A LOT
AND EVERYTHING.

273
00:16:00,035 --> 00:16:02,475
THAT'S WHY I'M A LITTLE PISSED.

274
00:16:02,475 --> 00:16:03,675
( Riehlvelt laughs nervously )

275
00:16:03,708 --> 00:16:05,975
Killua: THERE'S NO WAY
YOU CAN SURVIVE

276
00:16:05,975 --> 00:16:07,608
A FALL FROM THAT HEIGHT,

277
00:16:07,641 --> 00:16:09,441
SO WHAT DO YOU WANNA DO?

278
00:16:09,475 --> 00:16:10,675
Riehlvelt: CATCH ME! PLEASE!

279
00:16:10,708 --> 00:16:11,975
DON'T LET ME DIE!

280
00:16:11,975 --> 00:16:13,841
Killua: OKAY, THEN.

281
00:16:13,875 --> 00:16:16,341
DON'T WORRY.
I'M RIGHT HERE FOR YOU.

282
00:16:16,375 --> 00:16:18,141
( Riehlvelt screams )

283
00:16:19,541 --> 00:16:22,475
( screams )

284
00:16:23,508 --> 00:16:25,775
( stammering )

285
00:16:27,541 --> 00:16:28,941
Killua: DAMN IT.

286
00:16:28,975 --> 00:16:32,341
AT LEAST NOW YOU KNOW HOW MUCH
THAT HURTS, YOU IDIOT.

287
00:16:32,375 --> 00:16:33,641
♪

288
00:16:33,641 --> 00:16:35,141
Referee: RIEHLVELT IS DOWN,

289
00:16:35,141 --> 00:16:39,441
AND SO BY VIRTUE OF A KNOCKDOWN,
KILLUA TAKES THE VICTORY!

290
00:16:39,475 --> 00:16:41,341
( crowd cheering )

291
00:16:45,475 --> 00:16:47,375
♪

292
00:16:53,441 --> 00:16:54,441
( Killua gasps )

293
00:16:54,475 --> 00:16:56,375
Gon: NICE JOB, KILLUA.

294
00:16:56,441 --> 00:16:57,808
( chuckles )

295
00:16:57,841 --> 00:16:59,841
Killua: HEH. THANKS.

296
00:17:01,281 --> 00:17:03,715
THAT MEANS YOU'RE UP NEXT.

297
00:17:03,781 --> 00:17:06,281
HOW LONG 'TIL YOU FIGHT HIM?
10 DAYS?

298
00:17:06,315 --> 00:17:08,815
Gon: YUP.
IT'LL BE ON JUNE TENTH.

299
00:17:08,848 --> 00:17:10,848
Killua: JUST REMEMBER
WHAT WORKED FOR ME

300
00:17:10,881 --> 00:17:12,481
ISN'T GONNA WORK FOR YOU, OKAY?

301
00:17:12,515 --> 00:17:15,215
IF THOSE ELECTRIC WHIPS
SO MUCH AS TOUCH YOU,

302
00:17:15,281 --> 00:17:18,381
YOU'LL BE OUT COLD BEFORE YOU
EVEN KNOW WHAT'S HAPPENING.

303
00:17:18,448 --> 00:17:19,348
Gon: MM‐HMM.

304
00:17:20,681 --> 00:17:22,148
Killua: WHAT'S YOUR STRATEGY?

305
00:17:22,148 --> 00:17:25,148
Gon: OH, DON'T WORRY.
I THINK I HAVE AN IDEA.

306
00:17:25,148 --> 00:17:26,981
Killua: OH?

307
00:17:26,981 --> 00:17:29,981
YOU WEREN'T WATCHING
FOR NOTHING, WERE YOU?

308
00:17:29,981 --> 00:17:33,048
GUESS YOU PREFER COMBAT
TO OBSERVING, TOO.

309
00:17:41,848 --> 00:17:43,448
Hisoka: HMM.

310
00:17:43,481 --> 00:17:45,981
( chuckles )

311
00:17:47,781 --> 00:17:49,881
♪

312
00:17:51,981 --> 00:17:54,281
Cocco: IT APPEARS THAT
THE DAMAGE GIDO SUSTAINED

313
00:17:54,315 --> 00:17:56,815
IN HIS MATCH WITH GON
WAS SO SEVERE

314
00:17:56,848 --> 00:17:59,215
THAT HE HASN'T RETURNED
FOR TODAY'S FIGHT.

315
00:17:59,281 --> 00:18:03,821
Referee: THE WINNER
BY DEFAULT IS KILLUA!

316
00:18:03,855 --> 00:18:05,988
( crowd cheering )

317
00:18:13,188 --> 00:18:15,354
Cocco: AFTER LOSING TO KILLUA,

318
00:18:15,388 --> 00:18:17,288
RIEHLVELT'S RECORD
IS FIVE‐THREE.

319
00:18:17,321 --> 00:18:19,654
HE CAN'T AFFORD ANOTHER LOSS.

320
00:18:19,688 --> 00:18:23,321
AS YOU KNOW, AFTER FOUR LOSSES,
YOU'RE OUT OF THE CONTEST

321
00:18:23,321 --> 00:18:25,488
AND HAVE TO START OVER
FROM SQUARE ONE.

322
00:18:28,121 --> 00:18:30,321
HE MUST BE WARY OF GON'S SPEED,

323
00:18:30,321 --> 00:18:33,188
BECAUSE HE'S GOT
HIS WHIPS OUT ALREADY.

324
00:18:34,488 --> 00:18:37,054
MEANWHILE, GON ISN'T
CARRYING HIS FISHING ROD.

325
00:18:37,121 --> 00:18:38,654
HE'S COMPLETELY EMPTY‐HANDED.

326
00:18:38,654 --> 00:18:41,654
HOW DOES HE PLAN
TO FIGHT THIS TIME?

327
00:18:41,688 --> 00:18:43,488
Referee: BEGIN!

328
00:18:43,488 --> 00:18:47,288
Cocco: SONG OF DEFENSE
RIGHT FROM THE START!

329
00:18:47,321 --> 00:18:50,654
RIEHLVELT WANTS TO END
THIS FIGHT IN A HURRY!

330
00:18:50,688 --> 00:18:53,654
♪

331
00:18:53,688 --> 00:18:55,054
( Gon grunting )

332
00:18:55,121 --> 00:18:58,554
Cocco: WHAT'S THIS?
GON IS SQUATTING?

333
00:18:58,621 --> 00:18:59,554
Riehlvelt: EH?

334
00:18:59,621 --> 00:19:02,994
( Gon yells )

335
00:19:02,994 --> 00:19:05,494
Cocco: HE JUST
RIPPED UP THE STONE TILE

336
00:19:05,528 --> 00:19:07,561
WITH HIS BARE HANDS, FOLKS!

337
00:19:07,628 --> 00:19:09,794
( Gon yells )

338
00:19:09,828 --> 00:19:10,994
Cocco: AND NOW HE THREW IT!

339
00:19:10,994 --> 00:19:12,628
Riehlvelt: AURA BURST!

340
00:19:13,694 --> 00:19:16,328
Cocco: HE ESCAPED
IN THE NICK OF TIME!

341
00:19:17,394 --> 00:19:20,494
Killua: HE LEFT HIM
A WAY OUT ON PURPOSE.

342
00:19:21,394 --> 00:19:22,494
( Riehlvelt gasps )

343
00:19:22,528 --> 00:19:23,628
Cocco: BUT GON
ANTICIPATED THAT MOVE,

344
00:19:23,661 --> 00:19:27,194
AND HE'S ALREADY
ONE STEP AHEAD!

345
00:19:28,494 --> 00:19:30,494
Hisoka: WHEN YOU'RE
TRYING TO ESCAPE,

346
00:19:30,494 --> 00:19:33,328
EVERY FRACTION
OF A SECOND COUNTS,

347
00:19:33,328 --> 00:19:35,494
AND WITHOUT TIME
TO CHANGE DIRECTION,

348
00:19:35,494 --> 00:19:39,294
ALL YOU CAN DO
IS CONTINUE TO MOVE FORWARD.

349
00:19:39,328 --> 00:19:41,861
AND ACCELERATING
AS QUICKLY AS THAT

350
00:19:41,894 --> 00:19:43,861
WILL THROW YOU OFF BALANCE.

351
00:19:43,894 --> 00:19:47,794
HIS ONLY OPTION AT THAT POINT
WAS TO STOP THE WHIPS.

352
00:19:48,894 --> 00:19:50,828
THAT'S THE TIME TO MOVE IN.

353
00:19:53,894 --> 00:19:55,494
( Gon laughs )

354
00:19:55,494 --> 00:19:57,861
( popping )

355
00:19:57,894 --> 00:20:00,068
( Riehlvelt screams )

356
00:20:03,768 --> 00:20:05,668
( shuddering )

357
00:20:08,901 --> 00:20:10,601
Gon: SO THIS IS THE SWITCH, HUH?

358
00:20:10,634 --> 00:20:14,801
LET'S SEE.
I'LL JUST TURN IT UP TO THE MAX.

359
00:20:14,834 --> 00:20:16,101
Riehlvelt: NO! STOP!

360
00:20:16,134 --> 00:20:17,501
Gon: SWITCH IT...

361
00:20:17,568 --> 00:20:23,001
‐ Riehlvelt: STOP IT!
‐ Gon: ON!

362
00:20:23,068 --> 00:20:24,434
( silence )

363
00:20:30,568 --> 00:20:32,434
JUST KIDDING.

364
00:20:32,468 --> 00:20:34,101
( grunts )

365
00:20:34,134 --> 00:20:36,001
Referee: RIEHLVELT IS DOWN.

366
00:20:36,068 --> 00:20:37,801
THAT COUNTS AS A KNOCKOUT.

367
00:20:37,834 --> 00:20:40,101
THE WIN GOES TO GON!

368
00:20:40,134 --> 00:20:42,101
( crowd cheering )

369
00:20:42,134 --> 00:20:44,101
Zushi: HEY, GON!

370
00:20:44,134 --> 00:20:47,301
( Gon laughs )

371
00:20:47,334 --> 00:20:49,734
♪

372
00:20:49,768 --> 00:20:51,434
( Killua chuckles )

373
00:20:53,234 --> 00:20:55,468
( Gon chuckles )

374
00:21:04,108 --> 00:21:07,641
( clapping )

375
00:21:12,574 --> 00:21:15,341
Hisoka: SPLENDID. JUST SPLENDID.

376
00:21:15,408 --> 00:21:20,274
INCLUDING YOUR LAST TWO MATCHES,
YOU'VE MADE PROGRESS.

377
00:21:22,141 --> 00:21:23,408
YOU'VE MADE THE GRADE,

378
00:21:23,441 --> 00:21:26,608
SO SET THE TIME AND PLACE
OF YOUR CHOOSING.

379
00:21:28,141 --> 00:21:31,441
I'LL TAKE YOU ON ANYTIME.

380
00:21:35,141 --> 00:21:37,108
( Gon grunts )

381
00:21:39,641 --> 00:21:41,608
♪

382
00:21:49,408 --> 00:21:52,474
Narrator: THE STRENGTH THAT GON
DEMONSTRATED IN HIS MATCHES

383
00:21:52,508 --> 00:21:54,808
DID NOT ESCAPE HISOKA UNNOTICED.

384
00:21:54,841 --> 00:21:58,608
IT WON'T BE LONG NOW
BEFORE THEIR FIGHT BEGINS.

385
00:22:01,281 --> 00:22:03,448
( singing in Japanese )

386
00:23:11,254 --> 00:23:13,121
Gon: COMING UP, GON...

387
00:23:13,121 --> 00:23:14,121
Killua: AND KILLUA'S...

388
00:23:14,154 --> 00:23:15,654
Both: HUNTERPEDIA!

389
00:23:19,165 --> 00:23:20,131
Gon: I'M GON.

390
00:23:20,165 --> 00:23:20,998
Killua: I'M KILLUA.

391
00:23:21,031 --> 00:23:22,365
Both: AND THIS IS
OUR HUNTERPEDIA!

392
00:23:22,398 --> 00:23:23,798
Gon: TODAY WE'RE
INTRODUCING COCCO.

393
00:23:23,831 --> 00:23:26,298
SHE ANNOUNCES ALL
OF THE FIGHTS AT HEAVENS ARENA.

394
00:23:26,331 --> 00:23:28,998
Killua: OH. YOU MEAN THE LADY
WHO'S ALWAYS TALKING, HUH?

395
00:23:29,031 --> 00:23:31,298
Gon: I WONDER.
HOW MANY OF HER ARE THERE?

396
00:23:31,331 --> 00:23:32,631
Killua: YOU THINK
THERE ARE MOR‐‐

397
00:23:33,798 --> 00:23:35,698
♪

398
00:23:36,865 --> 00:23:39,165
Gon: NEXT TIME, "THE TRUE PASS."

399
00:23:39,198 --> 00:23:42,031
KILLUA, WHAT DOES "SO‐AND‐SO"
AND "SUCH‐AND‐SUCH" MEAN?

400
00:23:42,065 --> 00:23:44,131
Killua: YOU REALLY DON'T KNOW?

401
00:23:44,165 --> 00:23:46,298
IT MEANS SO‐AND‐SO
AND SUCH‐AND‐SUCH.

